            <scopecontent id="aspace_4bd275d8748ef8142bec2759cdbc1bf4">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series I contains photographs taken by Martin H. Schreiber of ranches, cowboys, and rodeos in Texas, Oklahoma, and New Mexico. Included are approximately 300 11 x 14 in., 30 12 x 14.5 in., and 200 16 x 20 in. gelatin silver prints.</p>
               <p>The 12 x 14.5 in. and 16 x 20 in. prints are duplicates of the 11 x 14 in. prints in the collection.</p>
               <p>Also present are four oversize prints, signed, used in exhibitions. A fifth oversize print may also have been used in an exhibition.</p>
            </scopecontent>
